{
  "stem": "23090.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there's-- the answer to your question is there was already-- if you want to call it-- a ghetto, or a community, a Jewish community, except that they just elaborated on the-- on bringing everyone else in and then closing it up.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I meant to ask you before to describe your apartment to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The apartment was a, a-- I think, it was, like, seven stories, or six, seven stories high.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do remember we lived on the third floor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always ran up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as a kid, we always had races trying to go up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no elevator, so we-- everything-- and for the elders, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you were out of luck if you were on the sixth, seventh floor, because it was pretty steep and-- It was sort of dark.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, there was-- electricity, in-- at the best of times, even before the war, was a luxury in, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So everything was not, you know-- everything was in terms of, of, of, of an experience, an adventure.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The suite comprised of a, a bedroom, a living room, a little what I would call, like, a studio, which the-- our piano was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the kitchen was in the hallway, like it was away from an apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the kitchen, as we knew-- the kitchen was a stove sometimes that you cooked under coal or under wood, and then your pots were on top of that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how we cooked in those days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was no exhaust.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the aroma would come for a block down the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a good aroma, so-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The apartment, it was, like, maybe three rooms, which was considered a, a fairly good, good, good living quarters.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
